author: Disney
description:
D23 Gold Members are invited to join Disney historians and critics Leonard and Jessie Maltin. With shared anecdotes and commentary from our hosts, learn all about the landmark New York World’s Fair that debuted iconic Disney attractions.
 
This Gold Theater will be a virtual reshowing of a fan-favorite panel from D23: The Ultimate Disney Fan Event presented by VISA last August: “A Beautiful Tomorrow – Just a Dream Away: Disney at the 1964–65 New York World’s Fair”! The panel features presenters Pete Docter, Becky Cline, and more — including a surprise from the Marvel Cinematic Universe! 
 
Join us on Thursday, April 24, 2025, at 5 p.m. PT / 8 p.m. ET for the latest installment of D23 Gold Theater!
